<h1>Ably Connection Example</h1>

<p>In this example, we demonstrate the the simplest way to publihs a message and receive a callback indicating success or failure to publish the message. See <a href="https://www.ably.io/documentation/realtime/channel">our Realtime Channel documentation</a> for more details.

<div class="row">
  <input id="publish" type="submit" value="Publish a message">
</div>

<div class="row" id="channel-status"></div>
